Margaret E. HASSENPLUG v. VICTOR LYNN LINES, Inc., Appellant. No. 9391. Circuit Court of Appeals, Third Circuit Argued Oct. 7, 1947. Decided Oct 9, 1947. Raymond A. White, Jr., of Philadelphia, Pa., for appellant. Russell Cooney, of Philadelphia, Pa. (Eugene J. Corrigan, of Philadelphia, Pa., on the brief), for appellee.

Before BIGGS, ALBERT LEE STEPHENS, and MARIS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the court below will be affirmed on the opinion of Judge McGran-ery, 71 F.Supp. 70.
